!! ---Changes + Updates---
* Now able to open+edit multiple tiddlers in their own popped out windows<br>^^my main motivation for the refactor^^
* Ctrl+Enter while editing a tiddler saves/closes the SideEditor
* Cursor focuses on SideEditor window when opened
* Added logic to prevent a tiddler from being overwritten
* Added new ViewToolbar and PageToolbar buttons to directly open tiddler editor in a new window
** Enable them in the [[$:/ControlPanel]] (Appearance->Toolbars->Page|View Toolbar)

!!! Removed functionality
* Cannot edit tiddlers tagged as `$:/tags/Macro` or `$:/tags/Global`
* Sidebar does not appear in front of SideEditor on hover

